parameters:
\nc<Customer>Mmm! That's good, that's good! Just need to raise the sound
effects here a bit more, and add some special effects.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>I-Is that so... You dreamed of becoming an AV director or
something? (Why do I have to watch a video of myself with
the customer...)

\nc<Customer>H-How did you know? Hmm... By the way, are we really going
to do it this time...

\nc<Customer>Right? Sigh... Guess I'll have to work hard and earn more.
The full performance with the filming option must be
expensive.
\nc<Customer>Of course! Videos are the best no matter the situation.
\nc<Saki>Uh-huh, I don't really understand, but... Good work today.

\nc<Saki>Somehow I've got a weird regular now... \bustMsgExp[1,
0]Well, it's okay! He doesn't seem like a bad person.
